::GoldenEye:;

She was flying around over the area when she saw Dollen walk away 
from the group.  She flew down to him and hovered on the 
breese. "What is going on?  are you going on a mission of some sort?"


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "dcoburn" <dcoburn@n...> wrote:
> ::Dollen::
> 
>         Dollen grumbled.  He looked at Reptilica, and then at 
Starscream, and then at Phobia.  When he looked at Phobia he 
sneered.  Then he looked up at GoldenEye, flying off.  He was going 
insane!!!  He couldn't take it anymore!!  Suddenly, his mind was 
blinded, by images of the beautiful bot he thought he was over.  He 
held his head in his hands, and fell down on his knees.
> 
>      "Uggghh, who are you!!!!!!  What do you want!!!!!!  I don't 
like you, stop this!!" He mumbled.
> 
>       He kept repeating to himself, "I don't like you, I don't like 
you, I don't like you......" He kept saying to himself, his voice 
drifting off into the air.  Then he suddenly saw, in his mind, all of 
the Predacons.  He was looking up at them.  They were laughing at 
him, laughing hysterically.  Then he saw GoldenEye, making out with 
another bot.  Suddenly, all the bots there started saying, "Reject!!  
A Reject!  A Reject!!  Nothing but a reject!!!"
> 
>      "Nooooo, noooo!!!!!  Go away!!!!  It's not true!!  
NOOOOO!!!!," Then, his mind snapped back to where he was, what was 
going on.
> 
>      "I can't take this anymore!!!!!  I'm sorry, fellow team mates, 
I have to get away.  I can't do this anymore!!  I need some time to 
cool off, when you see GoldenEye again, tell her I am gone, but I 
still want to be there for her," And with that, he turned, and walked 
away, into the shadows, and he couldn't be seen anymore.  
Unfortunately for him, he still had Phobia's baby implanted on him.
